Open Source Plan - Make Repo Public
====================================

Goal: user puts API key in .env, runs the script. No GCP, no service accounts, no Firestore.

PHASE 1: Remove all Google dependencies
----------------------------------------
1. Replace LLM layer (agent_config.py)
   - Remove: ChatVertexAI, google.auth, google.oauth2, GCP credentials
   - Add: ChatAnthropic (langchain-anthropic) as default
   - Add: ChatOpenAI (langchain-openai) as future option with direct OpenAI API
   - Config: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY or OPENAI_API_KEY in .env, that's it
   - Update model config for Claude (sonnet/haiku) and OpenAI (gpt-4o etc)

2. Replace Firestore memory with in-memory
   - Remove: langgraph-checkpoint-firestore, google-cloud-firestore
   - Use: MemorySaver from langgraph (already built-in, zero setup)
   - Conversations live in memory, reset on server restart (fine for open source)

3. Replace Google Cloud Logging with local logging
   - Remove: google-cloud-logging from error_tracker.py
   - Use: Python standard logging module
   - Errors print to console / log file

4. Clean up credentials
   - Remove: key.json from repo
   - Remove: all GCP_PROJECT, GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS references
   - Add: .env.example with just ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here
   - Add: .gitignore for .env, key.json, credentials

5. Update requirements.txt
   - Remove: google-cloud-*, langchain-google-vertexai, anthropic[vertex]
   - Add: langchain-anthropic, python-dotenv
   - Keep: langchain-openai (for future OpenAI support)

PHASE 2: Open source features
------------------------------
6. Network selector (mainnet + fuji)
   - Add NETWORK env var: "fuji" (default) or "mainnet"
   - Update RPC URL, chain ID, block explorer in tools.py based on selection

7. Contract knowledge pipeline (for ElevenLabs agent)
   - User inputs contract address
   - Backend generates knowledge script about the contract
   - ElevenLabs agent knowledge base gets updated

8. Transaction history tool
   - New tool: get last X transactions from the network
   - Agent can reference recent activity

9. Transaction suggestions
   - When user wants to transact, suggest via text agent
   - Voice agent is unstable, prefer text flow

Run setup after open source:
  cp .env.example .env
  # add your ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
  cd backend/orchestrator && uv pip install -r requirements.txt
  python backend/orchestrator/main.py
